I"7<h2 id="attendance">Attendance</h2>
<p><br />
You can see the attendance of all employees for respective pay period.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_68.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>You can edit employee details and attendance by right click on employee.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_69.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>You can also see the attendance of staff and workers separately by expanding the node.</p>

